&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-829600-2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;2&lt;/a&gt;. 图片来源见此：&lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/tuna-fish-bigeye-tuna-69317/&quot;&gt;https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/tuna-fish-bigeye-tuna-69317/&lt;/a&gt; 。使用pixabay授权协议。&lt;/div&gt;
