apsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">最近发帖</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="no-footer"> <div class="no-addendum"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">此处是留言板归档</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">添加新留言请下翻</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>如果你有什么想对我说的话可以放在这里，我会回复。当然也欢迎私信！可能会不定期清空留言板，所以请务必随意<span class="ruby">编辑<span class="rt">瞎 搞</span></span>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7027379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Keyest" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7027379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" >Keyest</a></span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>怎麼能如此高產呢？新人競賽有這麼一個競爭對手真的壓力山大啊！我也要加把勁了，恭喜！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wupaispanda" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5223229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Wupaispanda" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5223229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wupaispanda" >Wupaispanda</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>大概因为我是短篇写手…wupa的两篇文实在太长了导致我一直没看真是对不起，谢罪.jpg</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>同是新人，为什么你这么厉害？（哀嚎）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xanarchy-militia" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6910500&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="XANARCHY MILITIA" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6910500)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xanarchy-militia" >XANARCHY MILITIA</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>不厉害，我爬（。</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>中分作者页最速传说！！赶紧留个言，可惜没占到第一 期待你之后的更多作品！加油啊，黑键jpg ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedreamkiller" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5064505&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="TheDreamKiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5064505)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedreamkiller" >TheDreamKiller</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>你也搞快点，Dr.唐的人设我还等着看呢。</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>猛地发现星凌up了你的人事（双重含义）<span style="color: white">（此处可能道歉QwQ）</span>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" >Frozen starry sky</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>这竟然是我发布的第一个没被星凌d的界面，不胜荣幸！<span style="color: white">回白字：不，其实我不介意的，觉得文档不符合标准的时候就应该d。当然如果能留下改进意见就更好啦。</span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>是怪物新人！我爱了爱了——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" >BruceWu0463</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>没有没有，我写得像屎（。）前辈什么时候开个二阶段稿楼啊！</p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>二阶段只有半个月了还有稿楼的必要吗.jpg——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" >Kcorena</a></span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" >carter lu</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>前辈不要说笑了，上过精品的作者怎么能叫咸鱼（。</p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>你记错了吧，我没上过精品。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" >carter lu</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>会不会以为你的李家庄上精了（——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" >Kcorena</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>我记错了。太丢人了我爬！！</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>本来没想留言，但好像是第一次看到用留言板互动的形式，之前看到的都是别人单方面留言而作者什么也不说。这种互动形式真的有意思，一下子没忍住就。截至目前键斯特绝对可以说是高产高质量作者，与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼.jpg——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" >Kcorena</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>说来好笑，其实我是因为不喜欢评论区互动刷板，但是又觉得不回复诸位不太好，所以才设了留言板（。）这么一看效果还不错，欢迎大家以后继续和我留言板互动！</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4915183&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="hoah2333" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4915183)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" >hoah2333</a></span></p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>诸位前辈别硼了，人都被硼傻了，我一会就把这页归档。</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7027379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Keyest" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7027379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" >Keyest</a></span>：生存即繁衍，我即番茄汤。</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6213424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="ChroIridium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6213424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" >ChroIridium</a></span>：不由感慨自己是个什么样的贵物。</p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>前辈不要乱说💦</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/franz-ismal" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6351354&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Franz Ismal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6351354)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/franz-ismal" >Franz Ismal</a></span>：键鱼前辈真的好厉害……发文的速度还是质量啥的咱都望尘莫及……哎呀呀，嫉妒心，旺盛起来了！</p> <hr /> <p><strong>回复：</strong>硼砂禁止！我不是前辈💦</p> </blockquote> <div style="display:none"> <p>➡！！！以上是过往留言归档，添加新留言请下翻！！！⬅</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div class="no-addendum"> <div class="no-footer"> <div class="center-collapse"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">留言板</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">欢迎留言</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7027379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Keyest" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7027379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" >Keyest</a></span>：过往留言已归档，查看回复请见工具盒tab页。这里是留言板！可以用作：闲聊/建议/询问我给出评分的原因等等，我都会回复。此处会不定期清空，所以务必随意<span class="ruby">编辑<span class="rt">瞎 搞</span></span>。当然也欢迎站内私信！</p> <hr /> <p><strong>本次主题：</strong>提问箱！既然你路过了这个页面，愿意和我来玩Q&amp;A吗？可以隐去ID，我不会特地去查看编辑记录。</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <blockquote> <p><strong>Q：</strong>简斯特有最喜欢的中分作者吗，有的话是哪位？主站呢？虽然「最喜欢的中分作者」这种问题一般答案都是花子ejinfas这种大人物里选不过还是想问问顺便捧个场。</p> <hr /> <p><strong>A：</strong>看到问题的第一眼想要答Clef，定睛一看是中分作者…真是难倒我了。虽然之前的几年断断续续看过很多文章，但是大多是主站文档，而且从来没关注过一点社区相关的东西（是的，甚至包括作者）。很可能我看过一位作者的很多文，却不知道是同一个人写的…实际上我也不怎么知道花子和ej都写了哪些文章。如果一定要说的话，我在中分最喜欢的作者是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3728730&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="DouglasLiu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3728730)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" >DouglasLiu</a></span>，对情绪恰到好处的拿捏和描写真的正中我下怀。我在设计作者页的途中实际上也参考了道格前辈的作者页。（可惜还是没有魄力做到那么极简XD）<br /> 主站同上，没怎么关注过作者。但答案毫无疑问是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=213153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="DrClef" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=213153)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" >DrClef</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <blockquote> <p><strong>Q：</strong>B OR G?</p> <hr /> <p><strong>A：</strong>Neither！:P<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>At least I don’t like to define myself either way.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&gt;&#32;**Q：**这是用来复制的提问格式。</span></p> </blockquote> <hr /></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span> <div style="display:none"> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-774025-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. 俗称金枪鱼。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-774025-2"><a href="javascript:;" >2</a>. 图片来源见此：<a href="https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/tuna-fish-bigeye-tuna-69317/">https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/tuna-fish-bigeye-tuna-69317/</a> 。使用pixabay授权协议。</div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7027379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161432" alt="Keyest" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7027379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" >Keyest</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
