://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thewalkindude" >thewalkindude</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;The Z Team&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-avocado" >Agent Avocado</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-alias-fakename" >Dr Alias Fakename</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/superblobby" >Superblobby</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/golden506" >Golden506</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;The Underdogs&quot; (RE级“时间循环”情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drzinc" >DrZinc</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lantern2814" >Lantern2814</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" >Boogey_Man23</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/owldude" >OwlDude</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;[GOOD NAME]&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/niceguy44" >niceguy44</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oneguy" >OneGuy</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pamplemousse" >pamplemousse</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/emo-squiddy" >Emo Squiddy</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;The Metavengers&quot; (<em>n</em>级&quot;Naroclysm&quot;叙事修正情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr0shadow" >Dr0Shadow</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" >XilasCrowe</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drblackbox" >Drblackbox</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phantom-ink" >Phantom Ink</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Dumbsday&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/allmind" >allmind</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/squishnet" >SquishNet</a></span>，<span class="error-inline"><em>wi773</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ppangolin" >PPangolin</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Rookies With Heart&quot; (YZ- “敌意接管”情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/officer-wilson" >Officer Wilson</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/warren-shepherd" >Warren Shepherd</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/researcher-moore" >Researcher Moore</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/officer-rockwell" >Officer Rockwell</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Bright's Boys&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-j-willbur" >Dr J Willbur</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hawthorn" >Dr Hawthorn</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-t-ross" >Dr T Ross</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;No Waifu No Laifu&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wydness" >Wydness</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sergeant-stark" >Sergeant Stark</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gakupomurtagh" >GakupoMurtagh</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hylius" >Hylius</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;███████ ██ █ ██████ █████. ███ ██ ██ ████ ██?&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/biosciencescp" >BioScienceSCP</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/vizlox" >Vizlox</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadeye151" >Deadeye151</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;THE MADDEST LADDEST!!&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greypercival" >GreyPercival</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alluria-dragnil" >Alluria Dragnil</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/evergladez" >evergladez</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;redacc&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crows-nose" >Crows Nose</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-leadmon" >Dr Leadmon</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zetaalpha1" >ZetaAlpha1</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyneliex" >dyneliex</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Ocean Men&quot; (CD级“蓝移”情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cohost" >Cohost</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/evolation" >Evolation</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thomas-wall" >Thomas Wall</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Bonanza&quot; (LC级“有这么大？”情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/researcher-vellone" >Researcher Vellone</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taiko42" >Taiko42</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/loofa" >Loofa</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kendrioli" >kendrioli</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;Nobody Expected The Italian Inquisition&quot;</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordofthepotatoes" >LordofthePotatoes</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/urza-kan" >Urza_Kan</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/consistent-azurite" >Consistent_Azurite</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> <hr /> <div class="content-panel standalone series"> <h1><span>队伍名称: &quot;*Goat Noise*&quot; (Ω᧟级“末日瀑布”情景)</span></h1> <p><strong>队伍成员: <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notarealgoat" >NotaRealGoat</a></span> (<em>队长</em>)，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/slightlyrealgoat" >SlightlyRealGoat</a></span>，<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notquiteagoat" >NotQuiteAGoat</a></span></strong></p> <hr /> <h3><span>条目:</span></h3> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <hr /> <p><em>这个竞赛由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span>组织。 规则主要由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=451071&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="TroyL" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=451071)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" >TroyL</a></span>所写，并被<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span>略微修改。 计时器由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>所制。队伍中心格式为<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" >djkaktus</a></span>所修改。</em></p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/commintern" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1869497&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610161437" alt="commintern" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1869497)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/commintern" >commintern</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. 可以基于个别情况采纳在竞赛开始之前未完成的草稿。通常规则是草稿尚未完成一半； 如果你不确定， 请随时询问。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-2"><a href="javascript:;" >2</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为“Gestalt”，语源德文，意为形状。英语引申物体或经验中各部分为一有机之整，而不能割裂或分开来理解。在学术上，比如心理学，经常音译，如格式塔心理学。意译为中文一般为完型，整全。为了使末日情景为四字短语，这里采用意译。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-3"><a href="javascript:;" >3</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为“Hostile Demiurge”，Demiurge一般翻译为德谬哥，源自柏拉图主义中创造和维持物质世界的个体，对世界友好。诺斯底主义者使用这个词语同样指代创造物质世界的神性存在，但所创造世界并非完美，其本身也充满恶意。基督教也将此概念等同于邪恶撒旦。名字意译。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-4"><a href="javascript:;" >4</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为&quot;Large-Scale Aggressor Overrun&quot;，名字根据主站SCP-3534中“Involving the enslavement，reduction，or destruction of human life by an extreme number of Large-Scale Aggressors.”和“Instances exhibit characteristics of both reptiles and aquatic cephalopods (being extremely similar to UAE-Brasil-78)，and range from ~5 to ~300&#160;m in height.”意译。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-5"><a href="javascript:;" >5</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为&quot;Global-Incomprehension”，意译。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-6"><a href="javascript:;" >6</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为&quot;Multi-Universal Amalgamation”，强行意译。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-152190-7"><a href="javascript:;" >7</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>原文为&quot;Beepocalpyse”，&quot;Bee&quot;疑似和“b”双关，即将apocalpyse中a换为b。意译。</div> </div> 
